    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-8052-aed3-fce378c4fa35",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors propose a binary integer approach that can be used in the construction of a linear model. On a “second experiment”, the authors create a new construct that quyantifies justice. The experiments were conducted with 35 undergraduate students.",
