    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-8020-b1d4-daf57eb38ec9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors evaluate their approach on 4 indicators: time, mean deviation from optimal, mean student satisfaction and mean acquired knowledge. Method was not as fast as Rules-based solutions, but did achieve an optimum quite fast.",
